### Obtener todas las reservas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations

### Obtener una reserva por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/res-123

### Crear una reserva
POST http://localhost:8080/api/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accommodationId": "acc-123",
  "guestId": "user-456",
  "checkInDate": "2025-12-20",
  "checkOutDate": "2025-12-25",
  "numberOfGuests": 2
}

### Listar reservas por alojamiento
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/accommodation/acc-123

### Listar reservas por hu√©sped
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/guest/user-456

### Listar reservas por estado
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/status/PENDING

### Verificar disponibilidad
GET http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/availability?accommodationId=acc-123&checkInDate=2025-12-20&checkOutDate=2025-12-25

### Editar una reserva
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/res-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2025-12-21",
  "checkOutDate": "2025-12-26",
  "numberOfGuests": 3,
  "status": "PENDING"
}

### Confirmar una reserva
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/res-123/confirm

### Cancelar una reserva
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reservations/res-123/cancel